{
  "stem": "22972.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In early 1934, a friend of my father's was the first person I knew who was killed in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The early concentration camps were primitive in comparison to what happened later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Obviously, there were no gas ovens then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a quarry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a very, very wealthy man with a beautiful estate and a big factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they came and got him in the middle of the night, because some Nazi desired his home and another Nazi desired, coveted, this factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was taken to this quarry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was made to lift rocks and carry the rocks from one side of the quarry to the other side and back again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one day, he came upon a rock he couldn't lift.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a man stood over him and kept hitting him until he finally dropped dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in those days, the Germans were so civilized, they even sent his watch, and his ring, and his wallet back home to his wife.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't bother with those things later on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took the gold rings along with the gold from the teeth and melted it down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I was aware, whether it was '33 or '34, that if you said the wrong thing to the wrong person in school, in front of a budding Nazi child who had been already indoctrinated by parents at home, that they would come and take your parents and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, those days, they didn't bother much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They just bang, bang, bang and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll give you a wonderful example.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In about 1930-- my father's best friend in Berlin was assistant to Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
